    "accordion_content_EGhnWC": {
      "type": "accordion-content",
      "blocks": {
        "item_xPccUw": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "DESIGN",
            "content": "<p>Inspired by the sleek and sophisticated colors of the Bentley Stroller Trike, our Bentley Kids Helmets bring a touch of luxury to every ride. Designed to complement your child’s trike, these helmets feature elegant hues and premium finishes that reflect Bentley’s signature style. Whether matching their ride or making a statement, your little one will stay protected in true Bentley fashion.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_tVpzTf": {
          "type": "item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "SPECIFICATION",
            "content": "<p>REAR BRAKE: Yes<br/><br/>SEAT BELT: 5-point equipped with magnetic buckle<br/><br/>BASKET WITH COVER: Yes<br/><br/>FOOTRESTS: Basic (foldable) + accessory portable<br/>(for infants)<br/><br/>PARENT RIDE CONTROL HANDLEBAR: Height adjustable, two-position<br/><br/>WHEEL DIAMETER:<br/>12 inches (front wheel)<br/>10 inches (rear wheels)<br/><br/>ADJUSTABLE BACK SUPPORT:<br/>Two-position<br/><br/>FREE HANDLE BAR FUNCTION:Yes<br/><br/>STORAGE BAG: Compact, removable<br/><br/>SEAT COVER: Removable and machine washable<br/><br/>HEADRES: Yielding soft headrest with stitched Bentley<br/>badge<br/><br/>WHEEL FENDERS: Yes<br/><br/>USED MATERIALS:<br/>Iron, PVC, PP, ABC, TPR<br/><br/>FOLDABLE CANOPY: Two-position<br/>FREEWHEEL FUNCTION: Yes<br/><br/>SEAT ROTATING FUNCTION: 180 grees</p>",
            "page": "bentley-trike-assembly"
          }
        },
        "item_QMVwhR": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "HOW TO USE",
            "content": "<p>Your manual is enclosed in the box and provides essential instructions on proper fitting, adjustment, and maintenance. Please read it carefully to ensure maximum protection for your little rider.<a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6114e358197e4833a8f5707e54ca6439.mp4\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6114e358197e4833a8f5707e54ca6439.mp4\"><br/></a><br/>Download the manual <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0008/3368/3521/files/Bentley_Balance_Bike_manual_instruction.pdf?v=1741883330\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0008/3368/3521/files/Bentley_Balance_Bike_manual_instruction.pdf?v=1741883330\">here.</a></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_LLNwn9": {
          "type": "item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "SPARE PARTS",
            "content": "<p>Every journey deserves to be seamless. If any part of your Bentley Trike needs replacing, continue the experience by ordering an official Bentley spare part <a href=\"/products/bentley-trike-spare-parts\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bentley Trike Spare Parts\">here</a>. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_H639BW": {
          "type": "item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "WARRANTY",
            "content": "<p>If you experience any issues with your Bentley Trike within the <strong>2-year warranty </strong>period, we’re here to ensure a seamless solution. Simply enter your details in the form below, and our team will assist you promptly.</p><p><em>Please note : Warranty coverage applies exclusively to purchases made directly from us. If purchased elsewhere, kindly reach out to the original retailer for assistance</em></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
