      "blocks": {
        "toggle_QMVnUf": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/11.png",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Metal Bentley Badge",
            "text": "<p>A genuine metal Bentley badge is proudly displayed on each helmet, reflecting the iconic Bentley craftsmanship and attention to detail. <br/><br/>This luxurious addition sets the helmet apart, making it a standout accessory that blends safety with high-end design, perfectly matching the aesthetic of Bentley’s children's vehicles.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_nbemMh": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8.png",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Soft, Breathable Padding for Ultimate Comfort",
            "text": "<p>The helmet’s interior is lined with a yielding fiber breathable bottom cloth that provides superior comfort during use. <br/><br/>This moisture-wicking fabric ensures that your child stays cool and dry, even on long rides or warm days. Its softness adds an extra layer of comfort, reducing irritation and enhancing wearability.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_J7U8zB": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/13_9a2168d0-97b5-4189-85aa-008353e4905c.png",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Secure, Hassle-Free Magnetic Fastening System",
            "text": "<p>The Bentley helmet features a German-patented Fidlock magnetic fastener for quick, one-handed use, ensuring easy, pinch-free closure with top-notch security.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_UMznCd": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ergonomic_adjustable_seat.jpg",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Eco-leather & Ergonomic Adjustable Seat",
            "text": "<p>Features a carbon fibre inspired pattern that provides the perfect combination of style and comfort.<br/><br/>The ergonomic adjustable seat allows the bike to be tailored to suit your child's individual needs and grow together.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_6anEEk": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/airfilled_wheels.jpg",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Air Filled 12-inch Rubber Tires",
            "text": "<p>These rubber tiles further supports your child's comfort, helping balance out uneven surfaces and reduce overall impact.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_LnUXnj": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/10_96f27264-ef75-4e59-a4ce-4ae492082de3.jpg",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Replica Continental GT Mulliner Wheels",
            "text": "<p>The tricycle’s wheels mirror the iconic Mulliner GT rims with absolute precision. The signature Bentley logo sits at the center, encircled by the <strong>\"Bentley Mulliner\"</strong> engraving—just like the originals. <br/><br/>Adding to its exclusivity, the self-leveling wheel cap keeps the <strong>Bentley \"B\"</strong> perfectly upright, even as the tricycle glides forward. A masterpiece in motion.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        },
        "toggle_8kFNXA": {
          "type": "toggle",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/11.jpg",
            "badge": "",
            "time": "",
            "title": "Anti-Slide Pedals",
            "text": "<p>The new metal pedals with anti-slide surface design are the exact replica of the Bentley Mulliner gas pedal.</p>",
            "button": "",
            "button_url": ""
          }
        }
      },
